works.description: Another web page is showing our company logo and name and is also defaming our brand through the way they are displaying our logo at http://memegenerator.net/Windrawwin   This page comes out on the first page of Google search results when you search for our company.  This website is also spoofing its URLs to gain traffic by having our name "WinDrawWin" in its URL.  We have contacted the webmaster multiple times requesting the removal of this content, but have had no reply.
